text: People on the Top (, translit. Ahl el qema) is a 1981 Egyptian drama movie directed by Ali Badrakhan and is based on a story by Naguib Mahfouz. It stars Soad Hosny, Nour El-Sherif, Ezzat El Alaili and Mahmoud El-Qalaawy. == Other websites == * Category:1981 drama movies Category:Egyptian movies
title: People on the Top
